headline: FIS Triumphs with Two WatersTechnology Asia Award Wins
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., May 27, 2025--Global financial technology leader FIS® (NYSE: FIS) has been named as a winner in multiple categories at the 2025 WatersTechnology Asia Awards. FIS was named best ESG Data Provider for its FIS Climate Risk Financial Modeler and Best Reconciliation Platform for its FIS Post Trade Processing Platform.
